# B3: the dispatcher scrubs OUR dummy rows (GM + Continue) from NextUI's Recently Played /
# Game Switcher on every exit — the switcher dummy is the prime blacked-row suspect from
# the 0.9.1 Smart Pro field test. Real rows survive verbatim.
desc Continue dispatcher: recents scrub removes dispatcher dummies, preserves real entries
invoke ctpak
config paired
sdtext .userdata/shared/.minui/recent.txt	/Roms/0) Continue (LODORCT)/Continue.ct\tContinue\n/Roms/Game Manager (LODORGM)/Open Game Manager.gm\n/Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Mario.gba\n
expect_exit 0
expect_file_has .userdata/shared/.minui/recent.txt	✓ Mario.gba
expect_file_lines .userdata/shared/.minui/recent.txt	1
